scripts.setup-android: react-native bundle --platform android --dev true --entry-file index.android.js --bundle-output android/app/src/main/assets/index.android.bundle --assets-dest android/app/src/main/res && react-native run-android
scripts.setup-ios: react-native bundle --platform ios --dev true --entry-file index.ios.js --bundle-output android/app/src/main/assets/index.ios.bundle --assets-dest ios/app/src/main/res && react-native run-ios
